				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote7-10991_002_021"><a name="7-10991_002_021"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote7-10991_002_021">7.</a></span>
					<p class="">Véase <span class="emphasis">Adaptación a la vida misional,</span> (cuadernillo, 2013), págs. 23–49.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote8-10991_002_021"><a name="8-10991_002_021"> </a>
