					<p class=""><a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/nt/acts/17.32?lang=spa#31" target="_blank">Hechos 17:32</a>.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote18-10991_002_021"><a name="18-10991_002_021"> </a>
